<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>SurgeView Marketing: Reach New Viewers on YouTube</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="/public/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">

  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-primary text-white text-center main-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4 signup-header"><strong>Expand Your Reach on YouTube</strong></h1>
        <p class="lead">We place your video infront of real viewers, helping you connect with a new and engaged audience </p>
        <a href="#services" class="btn btn-lg btn-light">Start Trial</a>
          <!-- Large Icons Directly Below -->
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
          <div class="px-3">
            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="px-3">
            <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="px-3">
            <i class="bi bi-shield-check" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-5">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <!-- First Text Area -->
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <h3>100% Real Views &nbsp;<i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i></h3>
            <p>We exclusively use the official Google Ads platform so you will receive only real views and this keeps your channel safe with YouTube.</p>
          </div>
    
          <!-- Second Text Area -->
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <h3>Fast Channel Growth &nbsp;<i class="bi bi-graph-up"></i></h3>
            <p>Exponentially boost your growth over relying on organic placement. With our service you will get hundreds or thousands of new people seeing your content. This will lead 
              to more views and subscribers for your channel.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-5 bg-dark text-white">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Our Strategy Includes: </h2>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <!-- Text Side -->
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Consistent, Regular Growth on YouTube:</strong> we manage and optimize a paid advertising campaign to direct a steady flow of new, engaged viewers to 
                your content.  
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Safe Growth:</strong> Keep your channel secure and compliant with YouTube policies.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Engaged Audience:</strong> Connect with viewers who are interested in your content.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Fast Setup:</strong> Begin receiving viewers to your video within a few hours of signup.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Manage Your Account Online</strong> Use our online interface to manage your account, with no complicated process to cancel.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Icon Side -->
          <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
            <i class="bi bi-play-circle-fill" style="font-size: 5rem;"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="features-section" class="py-5 bg-primary text-white">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Features of Our Service: </h2>
        <div class="row align-items-center">    
          <!-- Icon Side -->
          <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
            <!-- <i class="bi bi-play-circle-fill" style="margin-right: 5rem;  font-size: 5rem;"></i>
            <i class="bi bi-camera-video-fill" style="font-size: 5rem;"></i> -->
            <i class="bi bi-youtube" style="font-size: 10rem;"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Views, Likes, Comments, and Subscribers:</strong> Our campaigns will delivery viewers to your video who are likely to engage with your channel further. 
                Number can vary depending on your content category and other factors.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Only Pay for Views: </strong> If you do not recieve a reasonable number of views we will issue a refund. This is due to YouTube's cost-per-view model
                where you pay for each view.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Placement on Home and Search page:</strong> Our service uses an ad type that allows your video to be placed on the homepage of people similar to your audience 
                and on the search results of keywords similar to your content. 
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Everyday Results:</strong> When working with our service you will recieve new viewers and subscribers (exact amount based on content) everyday.
              </li>
              <li class="mb-3">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                <strong>Views that Contribute to Your Channel:</strong> Views from our service are most likely to result in subscribers and future watchers, and are fully approved by YouTube.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how-it-works-section" class="py-5 bg-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">How Our YouTube Video Marketing Service Works</h2>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-1-circle" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
            <h5 class="mt-3">Step 1: Sign Up</h5>
            <p>Select a video to get started in your first campaign. This is the video that will recieve viewers and will be shown in the ad we setup for you.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-2-circle" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
            <h5 class="mt-3">Step 2: Select Plan</h5>
            <p>You can start off with our basic plan that will provide you around 100 to 200 new views a day. If you are looking for a more advanced level of service
              we have higher plans all the way up to our enterprise plan where you will get over 1,000 average new views a day.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-3-circle" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
            <h5 class="mt-3">Step 3: Campaign Starts</h5>
            <p>Once your campaign starts you will begin to see a daily inflow of new viewers and subscribers. The exact results will depend on varying factors such as your channel 
              category and content quality. </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-4-circle" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
            <h5 class="mt-3">Step 4: Manage Your Account Online</h5>
            <p>You can use our online dashboard to manage your account. Your YouTube analytics will allow you to see the results of our service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-5 text-white text-center bg-light">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
          <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-success btn-lg mx-2">View Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-5  bg-primary text-white">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Key Statistics</h2>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <!-- Average Views -->
          <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card border-0">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">30,000+</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Views a Month on Enterprise Plan </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Average Subscribers -->
          <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card border-0">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">1,000,000+</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Total Views Generated for Customers</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Total Campaigns -->
          <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card border-0">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">2,000+</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Total Campaigns Launched</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Success Rate -->
          <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
            <div class="card border-0">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">100%</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Success Rate in Views Growth</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="bg-dark text-white py-5 text-center">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="display-4">100% Guaranteed Views for Your Video</h2>
        <p class="lead">You will receive a number of viewers corresponding with each plan or be refunded</p>
      </div>
    </section>    

    <%- include('partials/faq') %>
    <%- include('partials/pricing_section') %>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>